{color:#505f79}any insert operation preemptively generates new ObjectID to check/ensure if {{_id}} exists in doc or not - but chances are that goes to waste. this waste is more pronounced in scenarios where _id is a mix of custom userland id and system generated one across collections of a db or even across documents of same collection{color}
